sources.title: The Live Wire (1935 film) Richard Talmadge, Alberta Vaughn | Romantic Comedy | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
A sailor finds an ancient vase on an uncharted island. He is later hired by archaeologists to lead them back to the island. They discover the temples of a lost civilization.

Director: Harry S. Webb
Writers: Leon Metzetti, Carl Krusada 
Stars: Richard Talmadge, Alberta Vaughn, George Walsh
Genres: Classics, Action, Comedy, Romance
